{"tid":1690035,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建立咗黃色經濟圈 係時候要黃色工會","createTime":"2019-11-03T06:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T11:09:25.000Z","uid":35136,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1bf9bd38c852c7522f777a58f8760eafce24b2","tid":1690035,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:22:28.000Z","msg":"呢一輪好多人講三罷 但點解好似冇聲氣<br />\n係因為香港一直都冇工會<br />\n個個都驚去到最後得自己一個罷<br />\n做咗出頭鳥就被人針對<br />\n但睇下其他國家係點搞罷工<br />\n係工會號召<br />\n透過工會知到有幾多個人同你一齊罷<br />\n如果有手足被針對被停職被炒<br />\n工會籌錢接濟<br />\n有咗呢個後盾先會有更安心咁企出嚟罷工同抗爭<br />\n85罷工好多打工仔都可能圍內有TG group 但太散<br />\n而家將呢班人用工會制度團結一齊<br />\n唔同行業嘅人想夾埋一齊 又可以有個工會渠道知道點聯絡<br />\n<br />\n而成立工會唔難 睇下職工盟個懶人包<a href=\"https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/unionsforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkctu.org.hk%2Fzh-hant%2FunionsforHK&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQVI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=f1ee18c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/unionsforHK</a><br />\n只要一隻領頭羊 (好大可能會被人針對)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/unionsforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkctu.org.hk%2Fzh-hant%2FunionsforHK&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQVI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=f1ee18c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/unionsforHK</a><br />\n有七個人寫個會章<br />\n就可以申請<br />\n<br />\n磚已拋 求玉"},{"pid":"024c9ff874e7e570772c83cf44a4aa0f11d3e6ed","tid":1690035,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:41:23.000Z","msg":"發夢中後排可唔可以click入黎睇睇 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到黎可唔可以緊張少少 審時度勢..<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57829f4a4cfb1554b4c0d6e46dab8080c1048463","tid":1690035,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8acc3a6cdac01f739d2e1899c5165c988cc49a3a","tid":1690035,"uid":3